#: templates/books/about.html:11
msgid ""
"Littattafan Hausa manhajar ilimi ce ta dijital da ke tattara littattafan "
"Musulunci cikin harshen Hausa. Manufar mu ita ce samar da damar samun ilimin "
"Musulunci ga al'ummar Hausa a duk faɗin duniya, ta hanyar fasaha ta zamani "
"da kuma taimakon Hankali na Wucin Gadi (AI)."
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:14
msgid ""
"Muna aiki don tattara littattafai 1,780+, fassara su, da kuma buga su a kan "
"yanar gizo tare da bayani cikakke da fihirisa don sauƙaƙe bincike da nazari."
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:21
msgid "Tattara Ilimi"
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:22
msgid ""
"Muna tattara manyan littattafan Musulunci cikin harshen Hausa daga ko'ina "
"cikin duniya."
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:26
msgid "Fassara Duniya"
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:27
msgid ""
"Muna fassara littattafai zuwa harsuna 10 don isar da saƙon Musulunci ga kowa."
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:31
msgid "Daidaiton Ilimi"
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:32
msgid ""
"Kowane littafi ana duba shi ta hanyar masana ilimi don tabbatar da ingancin "
"bayani."
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:36
msgid "Fasaha ta AI"
msgstr ""

#: templates/books/about.html:37
msgid ""
"Muna amfani da Hankali na Wucin Gadi don fihirisa, taƙaitawa, da samar da "
"SEO."
msgstr ""

